      {"id":"vpm4","difficulty":"medium","body_en":"Midpoint of $(0,0)$ and $(4,6)$.","body_he":"אמצע $(0,0)$ ו-$(4,6)$.","solution_en":"$(2,3)$","solution_he":"$(2,3)$"},
      {"id":"vpm5","difficulty":"medium","body_en":"$|(1,3)+(3,1)|$?","body_he":"$|(1,3)+(3,1)|$?","solution_en":"$4\\sqrt{2}$","solution_he":"$4\\sqrt{2}$"},
      {"id":"vph1","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"Prove $|u+v|\\le|u|+|v|$ (triangle inequality).","body_he":"הוכח $|u+v|\\le|u|+|v|$.","solution_en":"From Cauchy-Schwarz on dot product.","solution_he":"מ-Cauchy-Schwarz."},
      {"id":"vph2","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"Parallelogram law: $|u+v|^2+|u-v|^2=2(|u|^2+|v|^2)$.","body_he":"חוק מקבילית: $|u+v|^2+|u-v|^2=2(|u|^2+|v|^2)$.","solution_en":"Expand dot products.","solution_he":"פתח dot."},
      {"id":"vph3","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"State and use Varignon's theorem.","body_he":"משפט ואריניון — הצהרה ושימוש.","solution_en":"Midpoints of quadrilateral sides form parallelogram.","solution_he":"אמצעי צלעות → מקבילית."},
      {"id":"vph4","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"Find angle between $(-2,1)$ and $(3,2)$.","body_he":"זווית בין $(-2,1)$ ו-$(3,2)$.","solution_en":"$\\cos\\theta=-4/(\\sqrt{5}\\sqrt{13})$","solution_he":"$\\cos\\theta=-4/\\sqrt{65}$"}
    ]},
    {"kind":"pitfall","title_en":"Common Pitfalls","title_he":"מלכודות נפוצות","body_en_md":"1. **Adding magnitudes** instead of components.\n2. **Forgetting $\\sqrt{}$** in magnitude.\n3. **Wrong dot product** — multiply corresponding components and sum.\n4. **Angle in wrong quadrant** — check signs of components.","body_he_md":"1. **חיבור גדלים** במקום רכיבים.\n2. **שכחת $\\sqrt{}$**.\n3. **dot שגוי**.\n4. **רביע שגוי**."},
    {"kind":"before_exam","title_en":"Before the Exam","title_he":"לפני הבחינה","body_en_md":"- Add/subtract component-wise.\n- $|\\vec{v}|=\\sqrt{a^2+b^2}$.\n- $\\cos\\theta=\\frac{\\vec{a}\\cdot\\vec{b}}{|\\vec{a}||\\vec{b}|}$.\n- Midpoint = average.","body_he_md":"- רכיבים.\n- גודל.\n- dot לזווית.\n- אמצע = ממוצע."},
